OL,3,C'An extremely sad day': Thieves steal
OL,4,Chigh-value silver from Abbey
OL,6,FThe historic abbey and popular tourist
OL,7,Fattraction had to temporarily close
OL,8,Fafter tens of thousands of pounds
OL,9,Fworth of silver was stolen.
OL,11,FSherborne Abbey was broken into some
OL,12,Ftime between 9.30pm on Tuesday 6
OL,13,FAugust and 1am on Wednesday 7 August.
OL,15,FIt is believed that the offenders
OL,16,Fentered through the Abbey Close end of
OL,17,Fthe building and then exited near
OL,18,FChurch Lane.
