OL,3,C'An extremely sad day': Thieves steal
OL,4,Chigh-value silver from Abbey
OL,6,FReverend Martin Lee described it as an
OL,7,F"extremely sad day", saying the
OL,8,Foffenders knew what they were doing
OL,9,Fand where they were going.
OL,11,F"We are all deeply shocked by this
OL,12,Fcrime and now must work hard to deal
OL,13,Fwith the consequences and support all
OL,14,Fthose in our community who are
OL,15,Faffected by this act of desecration to
OL,16,Four beautiful Abbey," he said.
OL,18,F"It's quite clear the thief would have
OL,19,Fcome in before, and knew what they
OL,20,Fwere doing, they knew where they were
OL,21,Fgoing, they knew where the silver was.
