OL,6,F"These people would have been welcomed
OL,7,Fhere as we welcome all people.
OL,9,F"As a Christian community we have to
OL,10,Fmove on from that and realise that our
OL,11,FChristian faith is what's most
OL,12,Fimportant and that is not violated by
OL,13,Fthem because we're in control."
OL,15,FIt has been reported the silver is
OL,16,Fworth around #90,000 - but it is
OL,17,Fuseless to anyone and can only be used
OL,18,Fat Sherborne Abbey.
