OL,3,C'An extremely sad day': Thieves steal
OL,4,Chigh-value silver from Abbey
OL,6,FIt is also priceless for people living
OL,7,Fin the area. One resident said: "A
OL,8,Fpiece of silver that's been part of
OL,9,Fthe community for so many years,
OL,10,Fthat's something I found very
OL,11,Fupsetting."
OL,13,FA diocesan spokesperson described the
OL,14,Fchurch as one of the most "significant
OL,15,Fand beautiful" churches in England,
OL,16,Fsaying they were "deeply saddened" to
OL,17,Fhear of the theft.
