OL,6,FThey added: "Such actions are deeply
OL,7,Fupsetting for the community, who have
OL,8,Flost items of value to both the town
OL,9,Fand the Abbey. Our thoughts and
OL,10,Fprayers are with the community at this
OL,11,Fdistressing time."
OL,13,FDorset Police are asking people in the
OL,14,Farea to check their doorbell cameras
OL,15,Fand dashcam footage.
