OL,3,C'An extremely sad day': Thieves steal
OL,4,Chigh-value silver from Abbey
OL,6,FCommunity Support Officer Mark Jones,
OL,7,Fof Sherborne Police, said: "Sherborne
OL,8,FAbbey is a historic landmark of
OL,9,Fsignificant cultural value to not just
OL,10,Fthe town but the whole county and we
OL,11,Fare carrying out enquiries into this
OL,12,Fburglary to identify those
OL,13,Fresponsible."
OL,15,FAnyone with information is asked to
OL,16,Fcontact Dorset Police online or by
OL,17,Fcalling 101, quoting occurrence number
OL,18,F55240120614. Alternatively,
OL,19,Findependent charity Crimestoppers can
OL,20,Fbe contacted anonymously online or by
OL,21,Fcalling Freephone 0800 555 111.
